***Note**: This issue was originally created as [ARROW-11827](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-11827). Please see the [migration documentation](https://gist.github.com/toddfarmer/12aa88361532d21902818a6044fda4c3) for further details.*

### Original Issue Description:
The JSON parser should also support arrays of object, which are a common format for data in JSON (albeit not very efficient). 

```json
[{
    "a": 42,
    "b": true
}, {
    "a": 12,
    "b": false
}, {
    "a": 7,
    "b": true
}]
```
